text: sign up on Sparta time today if you need picture retakes. The session is called Picture Retakes. All 9th thru 11th grade students who did not take pictures on the initial picture day will need to get their photo done tomorrow. You can also have your picture redone if you were not a fan. These pictures are for yearbook AND your student ID. Seniors- please remember that these are ONLY the picture for your student id but you will still need to sign up for Senior Portraits on the Cady website if you have not done so already.
